Plot:
She is being abused, sexually harassed and bullied. Maybe because she is no beauty queen,
maybe because she is wearing a Primark bra or just because someone needs to be the underdog
in school. Elizabeth (18) is struggling. Especially because the cutest guy at College, Alec
(19), doesnt even know she exists. He only has eyes for Riley (18). You know the type:
she is stunning and life always seems to go her way. But when the roles are reversed death
is waiting around the corner... EYE CATCHER is a comment on the poignant life young people live,
in which your appearance is the most important thing and bullying is an every day occurrence.
EYE CATCHER is a dark film: an exciting, relevant thriller-drama about the society we live in today.
